<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[put cous cous in a shallow bowl]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[mix salt, water into the cous cous with your finger until all dissolved]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[mix in olive oil]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[steam over water, or the dish you are serving it with, for 20m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[pour back in the bowl]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[mix water into the cous cous with a wooden spoon until all dissolved]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[mix in butter and leave to rest, covered with a cloth for 15m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[put back in steamer for final 10-15 mins of main dish cooking time, then shape into a mound. Pour main in the middle and serve]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
